(27, 1, '2021-07-18 00:44:16', '2021-07-18 00:44:16', '<div  id=\"overlappable-4\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Overlappable\" data-id=\"overlappable-4\" data-export-id=\"overlappable-4\" data-category=\"overlappable\" class=\"overlappable-4 content-section content-section-spacing\" data-overlap=\"true\"><div  class=\"gridContainer\"> <div  data-type=\"row\" class=\"row spaced-cols text-center\"><div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"> <i  class=\"fa icon fa-clone large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i> <div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\"> <h5  class=\"\">FOTO UNDERWATER</h5> <p  class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan kamera underwater beserta operatornya. Untuk melengkapi foto tersedia juga persewaan properti foto underwater dengan beragam harga.</p></div> </div> <div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"> <i  class=\"fa icon fa-cogs large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i> <div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\"><h5  class=\"\">DIVING</h5> <p  class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan paket untuk diving lengkap berupa tabung oksigen, kaki katak (fin), wet suit &amp; googles. Tersedia juga paket underwater Walker Dive.</p></div> </div> <div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"> <i  class=\"fa icon fa-magic large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i> <div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\"><h5  class=\"\">SNORKLING</h5> <p  class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan alat untuk snorkling berupa pelampung (life jacket), kaki katak (fin), masker snorkle. Alat snorkling ini dapat disewa secara terpisah sesuai kebutuhan.</p></div> </div></div> </div></div><div  id=\"about-1\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\" data-label=\"About\" data-id=\"about-1\" data-export-id=\"about-1\" data-category=\"about\" class=\"about-1 content-section\"><div  class=\"gridContainer\"> <div  class=\"row text-center\"><div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\"> <h5  class=\"\">UMBUL PONGGOK</h5> <h2  class=\"\">Foto Underwater, Diving, Snorkling</h2> <p  class=\"lead\">Umbul Ponggok adalah wahana air pertama di Indonesia yang memberikan sensasi snorkling dan diving tidak di laut tetapi di kolam mata air alami yang dingin dan menyegarkan. Suasana kebahagiaan kita akan terasa lengkap dengan mengabadikan video atau foto underwater.<br ><br >Aktivitas seru dan unik yang ingin dilakukan adalah foto underwater dengan beragam tema dan properti. Pengelola Umbul Ponggok sudah menyediakan pelayanan jasa foto dan persewaan kamera underwater dengan operator yang berpengalaman. Kita bisa foto sendiri atau ramai-ramai dengan teman atau saudara.&nbsp;</p></div> </div> <div  class=\"row\"> <div  class=\"button-holder space-bottom space-bottom-small\" data-type=\"column\"> <a class=\"button color1\" href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" data-cp-link=\"1\" rel=\"noopener\">PROFIL BISNIS</a></div> <div  class=\"col-xs bottom-xs flexbox image-group-bottom-3-img space-bottom-xs center-xs\"> <img  class=\"left-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/computer-2569652.jpg\"> <img  class=\"center-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/apple-1838564.jpg\"> <img  class=\"right-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/laptop-2559795.jpg\"></div> </div></div> </div><div  id=\"cta-1\" data-label=\"Cta\" data-id=\"cta-blue-section\" data-export-id=\"cta-blue-section\" data-category=\"cta\" class=\"cta-blue-section content-section content-section-spacing-medium bg-color1 white-text\"><div  class=\"gridContainer\"> <div  class=\"row middle-xs\"><div  class=\"col-sm-8 space-bottom-xs\" data-type=\"column\"> <h2  class=\"\">Kontak kami</h2> </div> <div  class=\"col-sm-4 end-sm\" 