(29, 1, '2021-07-18 01:02:09', '2021-07-18 01:02:09', '<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Mengapa Kita harus berkunjung ke Umbul Ponggok </strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Ya, <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://umbulponggok.co.id/umbul-ponggok/\" target=\"_blank\">Umbul Ponggok</a></strong> adalah wahana air pertama di Indonesia yang memberikan sensasi <strong>snorkling</strong> dan <strong>diving</strong> tidak di laut tetapi di kolam mata air alami yang dingin dan menyegarkan. Suasana kebahagiaan kita akan terasa lengkap dengan mengabadikan <strong>video</strong> atau <strong>foto underwater.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[35,36,37],\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/belajar-wp_1-1.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"35\" data-link=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/?attachment_id=35\" class=\"wp-image-35\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/belajar-wp_2-1.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"36\" data-link=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/?attachment_id=36\" class=\"wp-image-36\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/belajar-wp_3-1.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"37\" data-link=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/?attachment_id=37\" class=\"wp-image-37\"/></figure></li></ul></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Bagaimana Kita melakukan ini semua di Umbul Ponggok </strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Aktivitas seru dan unik yang bisa dilakukan adalah foto underwater dengan beragam tema dan properti. Pengelola Umbul Ponggok sudah menyediakan pelayanan jasa foto dan persewaan kamera underwater dengan operator yang berpengalaman. Kita bisa foto sendiri atau ramai-ramai dengan teman atau saudara. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Apakah ada pelayanan lain di Umbul Ponggok ?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Pelayanan jasa persewaan lain juga telah tersedia : paket alat snorkling, paket diving &amp; walker, dan wahana permainan air. Sarana dan prasarana penunjang juga ada : tempat parkir, rest area, event space, toilet, mushola, area kuliner, kolam air khusus anak, homestay Tirta Mandiri.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":38,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/meet-developer-1-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-38\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Umbul Ponggok', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'umbul-ponggok', '', '', '2021-07-18 01:02:09', '2021-07-18 01:02:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coba_wp/?page_id=29', 0, 'page', '', 0),
