(51, 1, '2021-07-20 23:30:45', '2021-07-20 23:30:45', '<div id=\"overlappable-4\" class=\"overlappable-4 content-section content-section-spacing\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Overlappable\" data-id=\"overlappable-4\" data-export-id=\"overlappable-4\" data-category=\"overlappable\" data-overlap=\"true\">\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div class=\"row spaced-cols text-center\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"><i class=\"fa icon fa-clone large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i>&nbsp;\n<div class=\"\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">FOTO UNDERWATER</h5>\n<p class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan kamera underwater beserta operatornya. Untuk melengkapi foto tersedia juga persewaan properti foto underwater dengan beragam harga.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"><i class=\"fa icon fa-cogs large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i>&nbsp;\n<div class=\"\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">DIVING</h5>\n<p class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan paket untuk diving lengkap berupa tabung oksigen, kaki katak (fin), wet suit &amp; googles. Tersedia juga paket underwater Walker Dive.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding\"><i class=\"fa icon fa-magic large shadow-large-black round aligncenter reverse color1\"></i>&nbsp;\n<div class=\"\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">SNORKLING</h5>\n<p class=\"\">Tersedia persewaan alat untuk snorkling berupa pelampung (life jacket), kaki katak (fin), masker snorkle. Alat snorkling ini dapat disewa secara terpisah sesuai kebutuhan.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"about-1\" class=\"about-1 content-section\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\" data-label=\"About\" data-id=\"about-1\" data-export-id=\"about-1\" data-category=\"about\">\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div class=\"row text-center\">\n<div class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">UMBUL PONGGOK</h5>\n<h2 class=\"\">Foto Underwater, Diving, Snorkling</h2>\n<p class=\"lead\">Umbul Ponggok adalah wahana air pertama di Indonesia yang memberikan sensasi snorkling dan diving tidak di laut tetapi di kolam mata air alami yang dingin dan menyegarkan. Suasana kebahagiaan kita akan terasa lengkap dengan mengabadikan video atau foto underwater.</p>\nAktivitas seru dan unik yang ingin dilakukan adalah foto underwater dengan beragam tema dan properti. Pengelola Umbul Ponggok sudah menyediakan pelayanan jasa foto dan persewaan kamera underwater dengan operator yang berpengalaman. Kita bisa foto sendiri atau ramai-ramai dengan teman atau saudara.&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"button-holder space-bottom space-bottom-small\" data-type=\"column\"><a class=\"button color1\" href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\" data-cp-link=\"1\">PROFIL BISNIS</a></div>\n<div class=\"col-xs bottom-xs flexbox image-group-bottom-3-img space-bottom-xs center-xs\"><img class=\"left-img shadow-large-black\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/computer-2569652.jpg\" data-size=\"500x300\"> <img class=\"center-img shadow-large-black\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/apple-1838564.jpg\" data-size=\"500x300\"> <img class=\"right-img shadow-large-black\" src=\"http://localhost/coba_wp/wp-content/plugins/mesmerize-companion/theme-data/mesmerize/sections/images/laptop-2559795.jpg\" data-size=\"500x300\"></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"cta-1\" class=\"cta-blue-section content-section content-section-spacing-medium bg-color1 white-text\" data-label=\"Cta\" data-id=\"cta-blue-section\" data-export-id=\"cta-blue-section\" data-category=\"cta\">\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div class=\"row middle-xs\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 space-bottom-xs\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2 class=\"\">Kontak kami</h2>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 end-sm\" data-type=\"column\"><a class=\"button color2\" href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\" data-cp-link=\"1\">0810 0000 0000</a></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"latest-news-1\" class=\"blog-section blog-section-standard content-section content-section-spacing\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\" data-label=\"Latest-news\" data-id=\"blog-section\" data-export-id=\"blog-section\" data-category=\"latest_news\">\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2 class=\"\">Artikel</h2>\n<p class=\"lead\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div data-type=\"row\" data-dynamic-columns=\"handled\" data-content-shortcode=\"mesmerize_latest_news\">[mesmerize_latest_news]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"button color1\" href=\"[mesmerize_blog_link]\" data-attr-shortcode=\"href:mesmerize_blog_link\">LIHAT LAINNYA</a></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"content-13\" class=\"content-2 content-section content-section-spacing\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff; background-image: none;\" data-label=\"Content\" data-id=\"content-2\" data-export-id=\"content-2\" data-category=\"content\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"row middle-xs\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 bg-image shadow-large-black\" data-bg=\"image\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-7 full-col-left-padding full-col-right-padding\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"space-bottom-small content-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">&nbsp;</h5>\n<h2 class=\"\">Informasi</h2>\n<p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row spaced-cols \" data-type=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-6\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">PENGELOLA</h5>\n<p class=\"\">Badan Usaha Milik Desa (BUMDesa) Tirta Mandiri, Ponggok</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-6\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5 class=\"\">JAM BUKA LOKASI</h5>\n<p cl